# Git Commit Author

When creating git commits in this repository, always attribute them to:

- **Name:** Iman Suherman
- **Email:** iman.suherman@gmail.com

Do **not** change git config (`user.name` / `user.email`). Pass the author explicitly on each commit:

```bash
git commit --author="Iman Suherman <iman.suherman@gmail.com>" -m "$(cat <<'EOF'
Commit message here.

EOF
)"
```

Apply the same author for any amend or new commit created in this repo.
